
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Blocked</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #c0392b;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        ul {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .support {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Access Blocked by Security Policy</h1>
        <p>Your request was blocked by our Web Application Firewall for security reasons.</p>
        <p>Please try the following steps:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Clear cookies for this site</li>
            <li>Try using a different browser</li>
            <li>Open the site in Incognito/InPrivate mode</li>
            <li>Disable browser extensions</li>
            <li>Update your browser to the latest version</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="support">If the problem persists, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
